  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An addictive puzzle game inspired by <strong>BlackJack</strong>. Merge neighboring cards in the correct order to beat the Dealer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your arrow keys to move the cards. When two cards touch, they merge into one!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Try to beat the dealer in 50 hand-crafted levels; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Designed for experienced blackjack players and newcomers alike (you don't need to know how to play blackjack to enjoy this game!); </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A relaxing and addictive puzzle game.</p></li></ul>",
